`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Scourge_Of_Torak
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * c 'scourge of torak'

 This is a powerful spell used by the followers of Torak.  It will hit any
target in the room when it is used.  The caster will also be hit if he or she
is of good or neutral alignment, when the spell turns upon its caster.	The
spell causes damage and also inflicts a wave of maledictions, excepting the
"curse" spell, upon its victims.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
